* status or rights
Some commands are reserved to admins, some other to players, some
others to characters.  Take care of this.

* Separate command name and coded name
Allow accents to command names, while the coded name will not allow
it.

* List of commands
For each status or right, a list of commands should be available.

* Exit names and keywords
They shoul make sense from all the room they are linked with.

* Pronouns
A class, a function, or an array, could define all the pronouns for a
given gender.
